'''超新星殘骸G1.9+0.3'''是[[銀河系|銀河系]]內已知最年輕的[[超新星殘骸|超新星殘骸]]<ref>{{cite web | title = G1.9+0.3: Discovery of Most Recent Supernova in Our Galaxy. | publisher = NASA | author =  | date = 2008-05-14 | url = http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2008/g19/ | accessdate = 2008-05-14 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/668EkacGf?url=http://chandra.harvard.edu/photo/2008/g19/ | archive-date = 2012-03-13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。依據[[NASA|NASA]]的[[钱德拉X射线天文台|錢卓X射線天文台]]和[[甚大望遠鏡|甚大望遠鏡]]的資料綜合估計，這個爆炸發生在25,000年之前，而在140年前 (以2008年时计算) 訊號才抵達地球。在這之前，銀河系內已知最年輕的超新星殘骸是[[仙后座A|仙后座A]]，大約在330年前，殘骸的半徑超過1.3[[光年|光年]]。

==發現==
VLA的電波望遠鏡在1984年首度確認G1.9+0.3是一個超新星殘骸<ref>{{cite journal | author = Green, D.A. | coauthors = S.F. Gull | title = Two new young galactic supernova remnants | publisher = [[Nature|Nature]] | volume = 312 | issue = 5994 | pages = 527–529 | doi = 10.1038/312527a0 | bibcode = 1984Natur.312..527G | journal = Nature|date=December 1984}}</ref>，因為它的角值徑非常小，因此認為他非常年輕 － 年齡少於1,000歲（观测到的超新星的图像年龄少于1000岁）。在2007年，使用錢卓X射線天文台的X射線觀測，顯示較VLA較早的大了15%<ref>{{cite journal | author = Reynolds, S.P. | coauthors = K.J. Borkowski, D.A. Green, U. Hwang, I. Harrus, R. Petre | title = The Youngest Galactic Supernova Remnant: G1.9+0.3 | publisher = [[American_Astronomical_Society|American Astronomical Society]] | volume = 680 | issue = 1 | pages = L41–L44 | doi = 10.1086/589570 | bibcode = 2008ApJ...680L..41R | arxiv = 0803.1487 | journal = Astrophysical Journal Letters |date=June 2008}}</ref>。在2008年的觀測，進一步的驗證了它的大小仍在增加中，這意味著他的年齡不會超過150歲（观测到的超新星的图像年龄不会超过150岁）<ref>{{cite journal | author = Green, D.A. | coauthors = S.P. Reynolds, K.J. Borkowski, U. Hwang, I. Harrus, R. Petre | title = The radio expansion and brightening of the very young supernova remnant G1.9+0.3 | publisher = [[Monthly_Notices_of_the_Royal_Astronomical_Society|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 387 | issue = 1 | pages = L54–L58 | doi = 10.1111/j.1745-3933.2008.00484.x | bibcode = 2008MNRAS.387L..54G | arxiv = 0804.2317 | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society Letters |date=June 2008}}</ref>。

G1.9+0.3的座標位置在赤經17時48分45.4秒，赤緯-27度10分06秒，位於[[人馬座|人馬座]]，靠近[[蛇夫座|蛇夫座]]的邊界處<ref>{{cite web | title =  Sagittarius Constellation charts | work = The Constellations | publisher = [[International_Astronomical_Union|International Astronomical Union]] | year = 2008 | url = http://www.iau.org/public_press/themes/constellations/#sgr | accessdate = 2008-05-20}}</ref>。

==宣告==
NASA在2008年5月14日的記者會上宣布G1.9+0.3是銀河系內被發現的最年輕的超新星。在記者會之前的通告，NASA僅提示說他們將要''宣布天文學家在銀河系內尋找了50年才發現的一個天體<ref>{{cite web| title = NASA to Announce Success of Long Galactic Hunt | publisher =NASA | author = | date = | url = http://www.nasa.gov/home/hqnews/2008/may/HQ_M08089_Chandra_Advisory.html | accessdate = 2008-05-14 }}</ref>。''

